<h3>List Hygiene for Healthcare Practices</h3>
<p>Clean your list every 90 days. Remove:</p>
<ul>
<li>Hard bounces (invalid email addresses)</li>
<li>Contacts who have not opened in 6+ months</li>
<li>Duplicate entries from multiple intake forms</li>
<li>Anyone who has requested removal</li>
</ul>
<p>A smaller, engaged list always outperforms a large, unresponsive one. Email platforms charge by subscriber count. Removing 500 dead contacts saves money and improves deliverability for everyone else.</p>
